ROW.DATDSC: select mm 月份,sum(taxmny)/10000 本月增值税,0 a1,sum(lastememny)/10000 上月增值税 ,0 a2 from ( select * from ( select c.id mm,a.taxmny,lastememny from ( select a.yymm,nvl(sum(taxmny),0) taxmny,0 lastememny from tax_taxdata a,v_tax_company b,tax_compclass d where a.id=b.id(+) and b.typclsid=d.id(+) and nvl(b.typclsid,' ') like '[%HY]%' and b.id like '[%QY]%' and substr(a.yymm,0,4)= NVL('[%YYYY]',to_char(sysdate,'yyyy')) group by a.yymm ) a,v_mm c where substr(a.yymm(+),-2)=c.id order by c.id ) a union select c.id,elemny,lastememny from ( select a.yymm,0 elemny,nvl(sum(taxmny),0) lastememny from tax_taxdata a,v_tax_company b,tax_compclass d where a.id=b.id(+) and b.typclsid=d.id(+) and nvl(b.typclsid,' ') like '[%HY]%' and b.id like '[%QY]%' and to_char(to_number(substr(a.yymm,0,4))+1)=NVL('[%YYYY]',to_char(sysdate,'yyyy')) group by a.yymm ) a,v_mm c where substr(a.yymm(+),-2)=c.id ) group by mm order by mm
